ter 进行资源监听 | e2e_informer_test.go | TestInformerListerUsage |\n102: | T044 | 验证 Lister 缓存与直接 API 查询一致性 | e2e_informer_test.go | TestCacheConsistency |\n103: | T045 | 测试并发创建多个资源 | e2e_concurrency_test.go | TestConcurrentResourceCreation |\n104: | T046 | 测试资源不存在的错误处理 | e2e_error_test.go | TestNotFoundError |\n105: | T047 | 测试权限不足的错误处理 | e2e_error_test.go | TestForbiddenError |\n106: \n107: ---\n108: \n109: ## Phase 8: 集成场景测试\n110: \n111: | Task | Description | Test File | Test Function |\n112: |------|-------------|-----------|---------------|\n113: | T048 | 测试 AgentRuntime 与 CodeInterpreter 关联 | e2e_integration_test.go | TestAgentRuntimeCodeInterpreterAssociation |\n114: | T049 | 测试批量操作性能 (1000 资源) | e2e_integration_test.go | TestBatchPerformance |\n115: | T050 | 测试 Informer 事件处理 (Add/Update/Delete) | e2e_integration_test.go | TestInformerEventHandling |\n116: \n117: ---\n118: \n119: ## Verification\n120: \n121: | Task | Command | Description |\n122: |------|---------|-------------|\n123: | V001 | `go test -v ./test/e2e/... -run \"Clientset\"` | 运行所有 Clientset 测试 |\n124: | V002 | `go test -v ./test/e2e/... -run \"AgentRuntime\"` | 运行所有 AgentRuntime CRUD 测试 |\n125: | V003 | `go test -v ./test/e2e/... -run \"CodeInterpreter\"` | 运行所有 CodeInterpreter 测试 |\n126: | V004 | `go test -v ./test/e2e/... -run \"Informer\"` | 运行所有 Informer Factory 测试 |\n127: | V005 | `go test -v ./test/e2e/... -run \"Lister\"` | 运行所有 Lister 测试 |\n128: | V006 | `go test -v ./test/e2e/... -run \"Fake\"` | 运行所有 Fake Client 测试 |\n129: | V007 | `go test -v ./test/e2e/... -run \"E2E\"` | 运行所有 E2E 流程测试 |\n130: | V008 | `go test -v ./test/e2e/...` | 运行完整测试套件 |\n131: | V009 | `go test -cover ./test/e2e/...` | 验证测试覆盖率报告 |\n132: | V010 | `go test -v ./test/e2e/... -run \"Integration\"` | 运行集成场景测试 |\n133: | V011 | `go test -short ./test/e2e/...` | 跳过需要集群的测试 |\n134: \n135: ---\n136: \n137: ## Dependencies\n138: \n139: 确保以下依赖已安装或添加到 go.mod:\n140: - `go >= 1.21`\n141: - `k8s.io/client-go`\n142: - `k8s.io/apimachinery`\n143: - `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/envtest` (用于集成测试)\n144: - `github.com/stretchr/testify` (用于断言)\n145: - `k8s.io/api` (Kubernetes API types)\n146: - `k8s.io/utils` (Kubernetes utilities)\n147: \n148: ---\n149: \n150: ## Test Patterns\n151: \n152: ### 单元测试 (使用 Fake Client)\n153: ```go\n154: func TestAgentRuntimeCreate(t *testing.T) {\n155:     clientset := fake.NewSimpleClientset()\n156:     // Test operations using fake clientset\n157: }\n158: ```\n159: \n160: ### 集成测试 (使用 envtest)\n161: ```go\n162: func TestWithEnvtest(t *testing.T) {\n163:     env := &envtest.Environment{}\n164:     cfg, _ := env.Start()\n165:     clientset, _ := clientset.NewForConfig(cfg)\n166:     // Test operations against test API server\n167: }\n168: ```\n169: \n170: ### E2E 测试 (需要真实集群)\n171: ```go\n172: func TestE2E(t *testing.T) {\n173:     // Skip if not in e2e mode\n174:     if testing.Short() {\n175:         t.Skip(\"Skipping e2e test in short mode\")\n176:     }\n177:     // Test against real Kubernetes cluster\n178: }\n179: ```\n180: \n181: ---\n182: \n183: ## Reference\n184: \n185: - Delta Spec: `delta-spec.md` (AR-041 section, lines 1318-1726)\n186: - Client-go library: `pkg/client/`\n187: - API Group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh / v1alpha1`\n188: - Resources: AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter\n\n(End of file - total 188 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Tasks: AR-041 — E2E 集成测试\n\n## Overview\n\n| AR | Title | Module | Language | Size |\n|----|-------|--------|----------|------|\n| AR-041 | E2E 集成测试 | test/e2e | Go | L |\n\n**Design Stage:** [ST-3 completed]\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Clientset 创建与配置测试\n\n| Task | Description | Test File | Test Function |\n|------|-------------|-----------|---------------|\n| T001 | 创建 test/e2e 目录结构 | - | - |\n| T002 | 测试 NewForConfig 创建标准 Clientset | clientset_test.go | TestNewForConfig |\n| T003 | 测试 NewForConfigAndClient 使用自定义 httpClient | clientset_test.go | TestNewForConfigAndClient |\n| T004 | 测试 NewForConfigOrDie 正常情况 